     <br>- The rating obtained for models which have not yet been fully implemented, will have to be confirmed in the future by the application of the Standard Rating process to the corresponding implementations.
     <br>- For implementations or models which consider a developmental period, the rating considers the potential final <i>ConsScale</i> that they would achieve at the end of their developmental period.
